{"tid":645326,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"被警察攔車","createTime":"2018-04-28T04:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T05:06:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"677693437c2df5ccb031a4a94071cab1f3458a42","tid":645326,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180428/20374823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20374823&d=3B7IGMWn8NwjOBrodkRQj5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=e8d02255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20374823&h=2d7bf690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180428/20374823</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被警察攔車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180428/large/e8908a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Fe8908a.jpg&h=cdee2f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTwisted Truckers面書圖片<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n美國某州，凌晨一點多鐘，一個男子走上大橋，打算跳橋自殺。橋下是雙向的高速公路，橋面距離地面14英尺（427CM）高，男子跳下去不是摔死，便是被高速駛經的車輛碾死。警察一方面接近男子勸說，另一方面封鎖橋下公路，並攔下貨櫃車司機，向他們說明情況，希望獲得司機援助。<br />\n<br />\n貨櫃車司機仗義協助，十幾輛車迅速並排停在橋下，縮短了橋面與地面的距離。貨櫃車車頂距離橋面只有5、6英尺（一個成年人高度）男子若跳橋，受傷機會大減。<br />\n<br />\n由凌晨一點多至四點多，警察終於勸服男子打消自殺念頭，而貨櫃車司機也一直耐心等候。巨型車隊排列橋下，這真是世上最壯觀、也最溫暖的畫面，也許橋上男子因此而對這個世界重新產生留戀之情。<br />\n<br />\n同樣是警察攔車，香港警察逼巿民停車做人肉路障，引發死亡事故，事後被攔載的私家車司機更收到警察通知，有機會被告。而美國警察是向貨櫃車司機說明情況，徵得後者同意協助救人。做法不同、結果相異，境界更大不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n事件中的貨櫃車司機更被網民稱為英雄。在北美洲的高速公路有通宵駕駛經驗的人會明白，晚上其他車輛較少，是穿州過省的貨櫃車司機搵真銀的時間，黃金時間用來停車救人，司機們毫無怨言。若發生在香港，必定有司機鼓譟：「大佬你跳唔跳啫？阻住晒條路！唔駛搵食咩？！」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n<br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=3B7IGMWn8NwjOBrodkRQj5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=1cd62d26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a>"},{"pid":"c2694ef065276de09172976e9e79d9dc15aa29b7","tid":645326,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e0750a004c550c091e7d2412656ff6199e349d","tid":645326,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}